                  can be constructed that protect encoded quantum
                  information against shifts in the amplitude or phase
                  of a d-state system. Continuous-variable codes can
                  be invoked to establish lower bounds on the quantum
                  capacity of Gaussian quantum channels.}
}

@article{Michael-etal-Girvin-2016,
  title =	 {New Class of Quantum Error-Correcting Codes for a
