  annote =	 {We give a detailed account of the one-way quantum
                  computer, a scheme of quantum computation that
                  consists entirely of one-qubit measurements on a
                  particular class of entangled states, the cluster
                  states. We prove its universality, describe why its
                  underlying computational model is different from the
