  annote =	 {In this paper we introduce a general fault-tolerant
                  quantum error correction protocol using flag
                  circuits for measuring stabilizers of arbitrary
                  distance codes. Flag circuits use extra ancilla
                  qubits to signal when errors resulting from v faults
                  in the circuit have weight greater than v. The flag
                  error correction protocol is applicable to
